Package ar.edu.utn.frc.tup.lc.iv.services

Interface BillTypeService

All Known Implementing Classes:
BillTypeServiceImpl
@Service public interface BillTypeService
Service interface for managing bill types.

This interface defines the business logic for bill type operations, including adding, retrieving, and searching bill types.
